OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FA Scottish health board is set to
OL,7,Fbecome the first in the UK to roll out
OL,8,Fan innovative medical device intended
OL,9,Fto provide "greater care and dignity"
OL,10,Fto those experiencing miscarriage.
OL,12,FBeginning this year, the rollout will
OL,13,Fsee miscarrying women in NHS Greater
OL,14,FGlasgow and Clyde (NHSGGC) hospitals
OL,15,Fable to take home a "miscarriage
OL,16,Fcollection cradle", giving them a
OL,17,Frespectful way to manage their loss at
OL,18,Fhome.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@eO]wD@UOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
