PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FDesigned to fit beneath a toilet seat,
OL,7,Fthe device provides an alternative to
OL,8,Fsurgery and helps preserve pregnancy
OL,9,Ftissue for genetic testing, which
OL,10,Fcould offer insights into the cause of
OL,11,Fthe miscarriage.
OL,13,FThe cradle was designed by a team at
OL,14,FDignity Care, whose director Laura
OL,15,FCorcoran said she was inspired to
OL,16,Fcreate it after experiencing her own
OL,17,Fpregnancy loss.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,F"When I experienced miscarriage at
OL,7,Fhome, I faced an incredibly difficult
OL,8,Fsituation without the right support,"
OL,9,Fthe former NHS engineer explained.
OL,11,F"That deeply personal experience led
OL,12,Fme to design something that could help
OL,13,Fothers navigate the practical and
OL,14,Femotional challenges with greater care
OL,15,Fand dignity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@eO]sD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
