PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FThe cradle can be used at home or in
OL,7,Fhospital, and with features intended
OL,8,Fto reduce contamination and distress
OL,9,Fit replaces a process that many
OL,10,Ffamilies have previously experienced
OL,11,Fin facilities not designed for this
OL,12,Fpurpose.
OL,14,FMs Corcoran added: "This is about real
OL,15,Fchoice. When someone experiences
OL,16,Fpregnancy loss they should be
OL,17,Fsupported to manage it in the way that
OL,18,Ffeels right for them.
OL,26,@vD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,F"Our aim is to ensure people feel
OL,7,Fcared for, respected and supported at
OL,8,Fone of the most difficult moments they
OL,9,Fmay face.
OL,11,F"This is another positive step in how
OL,12,Fwe're supporting women to feel more in
OL,13,Fcontrol of their care, enabling them
OL,14,Fto have dignified experiences at home.
OL,16,F"It is also a holistic approach to
OL,17,Fcare, considering both a woman's
OL,18,Fmental health and wellbeing involved
OL,19,Fin miscarriage as well as the physical
OL,20,Fside."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
