PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FDignity Care is working with NHS
OL,7,Flaboratories to assess whether the use
OL,8,Fof the collection cradle improves the
OL,9,Fquality of genetic samples collected
OL,10,Fcompared with obtaining them through
OL,11,Fsurgery.
OL,13,FIf successful, it could increase the
OL,14,Fsuccess rate of testing without the
OL,15,Fneed for surgery, and help families
OL,16,Fgain insight into the causes of
OL,17,Fmiscarriage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
