PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FZara Gavin, who experienced a
OL,7,Fmiscarriage in 2021, is one of those
OL,8,Fsupporting the introduction of the
OL,9,Fdevice by the health board.
OL,11,FMs Gavin, who works as a scientist in
OL,12,FWest Lothian, said she began bleeding
OL,13,Fthe day before her 12-week scan, and
OL,14,Fwas later told her baby had died.
OL,16,F"I went to hospital for a scan and
OL,17,Fthey confirmed we had lost the baby,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,F"I was given several leaflets and sent
OL,7,Fhome, but I had no real understanding
OL,8,Fof what I was about to go through or
OL,9,Fwhat to expect."
OL,11,FShe miscarried later that night at
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,F"I was in agony for hours and I didn't
OL,15,Frealise the pain I was experiencing
OL,16,Fwere contractions," she said.
OL,18,F"I also didn't realise that when the
OL,19,Fpain stopped, it meant I had passed
OL,20,Fthe baby.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@PO]vD@AOUxD@SO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
