PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,F"Having clearer information and the
OL,7,Foption of something like the cradle
OL,8,Fwould give families more
OL,9,Funderstanding."
OL,11,FNikki Harvey, lead nurse gynaecology
OL,12,Fand early pregnancy at NHSGGC, said:
OL,13,F"We understand how upsetting a
OL,14,Fmiscarriage can be for many women and
OL,15,Fwe have processes in place to ensure
OL,16,Fthey feel supported when this happens
OL,17,Fto them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@OO]uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
