PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,F"We're pleased to be gradually
OL,7,Fintroducing the collection cradle,
OL,8,Foffering it to women where it is
OL,9,Fclinically appropriate, starting with
OL,10,Fthe Royal Alexandra Hospital and then
OL,11,Finto our other sites."
OL,13,FBy reducing the need for surgery the
OL,14,Fdevice has also been shown to save
OL,15,Fmoney, with an independent health
OL,16,Feconomic report suggesting it could
OL,17,Fsave between #6.7 million and #11.2
OL,18,Fmillion annually, freeing up an
OL,19,Festimated 7,300 to 12,000 surgery
OL,20,Fslots.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
