PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FResearch shows one in three women
OL,7,Fexperiencing pregnancy loss attend
OL,8,FA&E, yet one in five are turned away
OL,9,Fwithout treatment ` indicating many
OL,10,Ffamilies need compassionate support
OL,11,Fand practical guidance as much as
OL,12,Fclinical intervention.
OL,14,FThe rollout will begin at the Royal
OL,15,FMaternity Unit before moving on to the
OL,16,FQueen Elizabeth University Hospital
OL,17,Fand Princess Royal Maternity Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1774400571
OL,3,CHealth board becomes first in UK to
OL,4,Croll out miscarriage cradle kits
OL,6,FWhile a small number of hospitals have
OL,7,Fused the device elsewhere in the UK,
OL,8,FGlasgow's commitment represents the
OL,9,Ffirst full integration across multiple
OL,10,Fhospital sites, with guaranteed access
OL,11,Ffor eligible patients over the coming
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,FThe move is supported by #1.5 million
OL,15,Fin Scottish Government funding
OL,16,Fdedicated to compassionate miscarriage
OL,17,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
